Patch Set 1: Verified-1

(1 comment)

Zuul encountered a syntax error while parsing its configuration in the
repo openstack/glance on branch stable/stein.  The error was:

  The project template "openstack-python3-stein-jobs" was not found.

The error appears in the following project stanza:

  project:
      templates:
        - check-requirements
        - integrated-gate
        - integrated-gate-py3
        - openstack-lower-constraints-jobs
        - openstack-python-jobs
        - openstack-python3-stein-jobs
        - periodic-stable-jobs
        - publish-openstack-docs-pti
        - release-notes-jobs-python3
      check:
        jobs:
          - openstack-tox-functional
          - openstack-tox-functional-py36
          - glance-eventlet-ssl-handshake-broken-py3:
              voting: false
          - devstack-plugin-ceph-tempest:
              voting: false
              irrelevant-files:

          # branch as well, which is pointless because these libraries are
